OL,5,G2310 Hockney: Double Portrait
OL,6,     FAn intimate documentary profile of
OL,7,     Fartist David Hockney as he returns
OL,8,     Fto the theme of double portraits,
OL,9,     Fthree decades after his iconic Mr
OL,10,     Fand Mrs Clark and Percy. From
OL,11,     F2003.
OL,12,G0000 Face to Face with David Hockney
OL,13,     FIn an interview first broadcast in
OL,14,     F1996, artist David Hockney talks
OL,15,     Fto Jeremy Isaacs about painting,
OL,16,     Fdesigning for the opera and his
OL,17,     Fgrowing deafness.
